{"word":"G2626 - κατακλύζω - kataklýzō - kat-ak-lood'-zo - Overflow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατακλύζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kataklýzō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ak-lood'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Overflow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழி, வெள்ளம்"},{"paragraph":"to overwhelm with water, to submerge, deluge"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2830 - κλύδων - klýdōn - kloo'-dohn/2830\">G2830</a>; to <i>dash</i> (<i>wash</i>) <i>down</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>deluge:</i> - overflow.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}